    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Oct 14 and 16 articles and Oct 16 chart that misstated Texaco Inc and Chevron Corp 1999 combined revenue, which totaled $85 billion</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Articles on Oct. 14 and 16 and a front-page chart on Oct. 16 about the acquisition of Texaco Inc. by the Chevron Corporation misstated the total 1999 revenue for the companies. Including their Caltex joint venture, which sells petroleum products in Asia, the combined revenue for the companies was $85 billion, not $66.5 billion.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
